options: use-new-api: true on place: if player has permission "minecraft.command.op": continue else: wait 20 seconds destroy the placed block play effect "ENDER_DRAGON_DEATH" at location of the placed block on break: if block is part of region "spawn": cancel event send "Tento blok nelze ničit." else: continue on entity explode: if entity is a "ender_crystal": if player has permission "minecraft.command.op": continue else: cancel event on break of stone: if player has permission "minecraft.command.op": set {_block} to the broken block wait 20 seconds destroy {_block} play effect "ENDER_DRAGON_DEATH" at location of {_block} visible to all players else: send "Nemáš dostatečné oprávnění k ničení bloků." on use of tnt: if player has permission "minecraft.command.op": explode tnt else: send "Nemáš dostatečné oprávnění k používání TNT."
